# About the cover image

## Original photo

The original Sagrada Familia photo is distributed at
[commons.wikipedia.org](https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:Sagrada_Familia_(July_2022)_08.jpg).
Its license is shown in the last section.

## Modification

NACAMURA Mitsuhiro modified the original photo by cropping, downsizing, and
adding a text logo.

